'''Garphyttan National Park''' ({{lang-sv|Garphyttans nationalpark}}) is a [[Sweden|Swedish]] [[national park]] in [[Kilsbergen]] west of [[Örebro]] in [[Lekeberg Municipality]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://sverigesnationalparker.se/en/choose-park---list/garphyttan-national-park/#.VqbNaVKy4Qw |title=Garphyttan national park &#124; Choose Park - List &#124; Sweden's national parks |publisher=Sverigesnationalparker.se |date= |accessdate=2016-01-26}}</ref> The national park has an area of {{convert|1.11|km2|mi2|abbr=on}}<ref name="naturvårdsverket">{{cite web | title=Garphyttan National Park | url=http://www.naturvardsverket.se/en/In-English/Menu/Enjoying-nature/National-parks-and-other-places-worth-visiting/National-Parks-in-Sweden/Garphyttan-National-Park/ | publisher=[[Environmental Protection Agency (Sweden)|Naturvårdsverket]] | accessdate=2009-02-26 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090404174552/http://www.naturvardsverket.se/en/In-English/Menu/Enjoying-nature/National-parks-and-other-places-worth-visiting/National-Parks-in-Sweden/Garphyttan-National-Park/ | archivedate=2009-04-04 | df= }}</ref> and was established in 1909 as the first of its kind in [[Sweden]],<ref name="naturvårdsverket" /> but was in existence as early as 1857.<ref>{{cite journal|title= Botaniska notiser: för år|journal=[[Botaniska Notiser]]|volume=103|author=Lunds botaniska förening|publisher=O. Nordstedt och A. Falck|year=1857}}</ref>
{{Swedish National Parks|float=none}}

