'''Kwansŏ''' is the name of a region that coincides with the former [[Pyongan Province]] in what is now [[North Korea]]. The region includes the modern-day provinces of [[Chagang Province|Chagang]], [[South Pyongan Province|South Pyongan]] and [[North Pyongan Province|North Pyongan]] and the self-governing cities of [[Nampo]] and [[Pyongyang]].

